1
00:00:06,140 --> 00:00:08,540
=Fireworks=

2
00:00:08,540 --> 00:00:10,860
=Episode 15=

3
00:00:14,540 --> 00:00:16,340
(Inheritance Donation Agreement)

4
00:00:20,120 --> 00:00:20,920
Qiao Wenjun!

5
00:00:21,679 --> 00:00:22,399
Qiao Wenjun!

6
00:00:22,839 --> 00:00:23,679
Aunt Wenjun!

7
00:00:24,280 --> 00:00:25,120
Aunt Wenjun!

8
00:00:29,120 --> 00:00:29,920
Aunt Wenjun.

9
00:00:43,439 --> 00:00:44,960
Why are you here?

10
00:00:45,679 --> 00:00:46,479
Duan Yiran...

11
00:00:47,960 --> 00:00:50,119
She asked me to come see you.

12
00:00:52,840 --> 00:00:54,000
Why?

13
00:00:56,479 --> 00:00:58,679
Why won't any of you punish me?

14
00:01:00,320 --> 00:01:02,280
Dad said he loved me,

15
00:01:03,520 --> 00:01:05,879
but I did so many terrible things.

16
00:01:06,400 --> 00:01:07,959
I almost killed him.

17
00:01:08,799 --> 00:01:12,040
My obsession and stubbornness

18
00:01:12,680 --> 00:01:16,560
also hurt Yiran and all of you.

19
00:01:19,719 --> 00:01:23,920
Back when Zhenxuan
left home to start a business,

20
00:01:24,280 --> 00:01:26,120
I sabotaged him

21
00:01:26,120 --> 00:01:29,480
and got him into massive debt.

22
00:01:30,599 --> 00:01:31,640
It was you!

23
00:01:33,040 --> 00:01:34,359
So it really was you!

24
00:01:35,519 --> 00:01:38,799
I didn't think
it would lead to his death.

25
00:01:39,760 --> 00:01:44,599
I also didn't think it would
leave you without a father.

26
00:01:48,400 --> 00:01:50,799
I've done so many wrongs

27
00:01:52,680 --> 00:01:54,439
and caused so much harm,

28
00:01:56,040 --> 00:01:58,200
but none of you punish me.

29
00:01:59,680 --> 00:02:00,719
It just

30
00:02:02,560 --> 00:02:06,640
makes it harder
for me to live with myself.

31
00:02:08,280 --> 00:02:13,240
Then let guilt
and regret be your punishment.

32
00:02:13,680 --> 00:02:15,800
Don't you hate me?

33
00:02:17,639 --> 00:02:18,680
I do.

34
00:02:20,759 --> 00:02:24,680
But I'm not the one
who decides your punishment.

35
00:02:30,420 --> 00:02:33,340
(Qiao Wenjun, Duan Yiran,
and Bai Niansheng face justice.)

36
00:02:52,919 --> 00:02:55,439
Qiao Wenjun's case is closed.

37
00:02:56,240 --> 00:02:57,360
She turned herself in.

38
00:02:58,120 --> 00:02:59,639
She actually woke up to what she did.

39
00:03:00,360 --> 00:03:03,400
She's not actually

40
00:03:04,120 --> 00:03:06,159
cold-hearted.

41
00:03:07,000 --> 00:03:10,800
She was just never truly loved,

42
00:03:11,400 --> 00:03:13,080
so she never learned how to love.

43
00:03:13,919 --> 00:03:15,599
She took how Grandpa treated her

44
00:03:16,120 --> 00:03:18,159
and repeated it
in a worse way on Duan Yiran.

45
00:03:18,919 --> 00:03:20,879
That's what led to all of this.

46
00:03:21,479 --> 00:03:24,000
Do you hate her?

47
00:03:24,639 --> 00:03:25,439
Yes.

48
00:03:26,960 --> 00:03:28,960
Hate can last longer than love,

49
00:03:28,960 --> 00:03:32,319
but love is harder to forget.

50
00:03:32,680 --> 00:03:33,759
Then do you love me?

51
00:03:35,039 --> 00:03:36,680
What?

52
00:03:37,199 --> 00:03:39,360
I didn't catch that.

53
00:03:42,280 --> 00:03:43,080
I asked

54
00:03:44,439 --> 00:03:45,560
if you love me.

55
00:03:47,479 --> 00:03:49,080
What? I can't hear you.

56
00:03:52,360 --> 00:03:53,639
Then I'll just take it as a yes.

57
00:03:55,840 --> 00:03:58,360
Nian, I love you.

58
00:03:59,360 --> 00:04:00,639
We haven't...

59
00:04:06,719 --> 00:04:07,520
You...

60
00:04:07,840 --> 00:04:08,639
You...

61
00:04:09,159 --> 00:04:11,000
I bought your favorite snacks.

62
00:04:11,639 --> 00:04:12,439
Want some?

63
00:04:16,519 --> 00:04:18,079
Don't think snacks

64
00:04:18,079 --> 00:04:19,399
will make me forgive you.

65
00:04:21,500 --> 00:04:22,600
I'm going to wash my hands.

66
00:04:31,079 --> 00:04:32,920
Doctor, how is she?

67
00:04:33,120 --> 00:04:34,160
Is it serious?

68
00:04:34,639 --> 00:04:35,560
It's not serious.

69
00:04:35,839 --> 00:04:36,879
Her gastritis is

70
00:04:36,879 --> 00:04:39,160
mainly caused
by stress and lack of sleep.

71
00:04:39,519 --> 00:04:40,959
Just eat normally

72
00:04:41,079 --> 00:04:42,439
and rest well.

73
00:04:44,079 --> 00:04:46,600
Yunyi, you heard the doctor.

74
00:04:46,839 --> 00:04:48,120
Eat properly

75
00:04:48,720 --> 00:04:49,839
and stop

76
00:04:49,839 --> 00:04:50,879
stressing yourself out.

77
00:04:53,600 --> 00:04:54,759
Thank you, doctor.

78
00:04:55,560 --> 00:04:56,759
- No problem.
- Thank you.

79
00:04:56,759 --> 00:04:57,560
Take care.

80
00:05:01,920 --> 00:05:02,720
Here.

81
00:05:06,040 --> 00:05:07,199
(It's Nian, my daughter!)

82
00:05:07,879 --> 00:05:08,560
Nian!

83
00:05:09,720 --> 00:05:10,839
(Mom?)

84
00:05:16,560 --> 00:05:17,720
It's Mom!

85
00:05:30,639 --> 00:05:32,399
Shut up!

86
00:05:34,800 --> 00:05:36,959
You don't want
Qiao Nian to be okay, do you?

87
00:05:39,959 --> 00:05:41,759
You shouldn't have spoken.

88
00:05:54,319 --> 00:05:55,120
Get inside!

89
00:05:57,800 --> 00:05:59,040
I told you!

90
00:05:59,240 --> 00:06:00,279
You're not allowed

91
00:06:00,279 --> 00:06:01,360
to see Qiao Nian

92
00:06:01,360 --> 00:06:02,920
without my permission!

93
00:06:03,360 --> 00:06:04,040
Do you hear me?

94
00:06:04,160 --> 00:06:05,120
Do you hear me?

95
00:06:05,120 --> 00:06:05,959
Ah!

96
00:06:09,720 --> 00:06:11,000
You bit me?

97
00:06:11,000 --> 00:06:12,519
I...

98
00:06:21,480 --> 00:06:23,439
I acted on impulse.

99
00:06:24,360 --> 00:06:26,399
Don't worry,

100
00:06:27,800 --> 00:06:30,040
I won't do anything to Qiao Nian.

101
00:06:30,920 --> 00:06:31,959
As for you,

102
00:06:32,600 --> 00:06:34,120
your stomach keeps acting up

103
00:06:34,279 --> 00:06:35,839
and you're always in the hospital.

104
00:06:37,800 --> 00:06:40,079
Take better care of yourself.

105
00:06:41,480 --> 00:06:43,000
I don't want to lose you.

106
00:06:44,040 --> 00:06:46,480
I want to spend
the rest of my life with you.

107
00:06:48,199 --> 00:06:49,160
Disgusting.

108
00:06:50,839 --> 00:06:52,079
Say whatever you want.

109
00:07:04,920 --> 00:07:06,759
Mr. Jiang, something's wrong. Look.

110
00:07:10,620 --> 00:07:13,380
(Breaking news: Qiao Group chairman
is alive. Truth revealed.)

111
00:07:14,160 --> 00:07:19,759
(What? He's still alive?
This just got complicated.)

112
00:07:30,319 --> 00:07:31,120
What's wrong?

113
00:07:32,639 --> 00:07:35,959
I think I just heard Mom's voice.

114
00:07:36,160 --> 00:07:37,040
Your mom?

115
00:07:37,160 --> 00:07:37,959
Yeah.

116
00:07:41,079 --> 00:07:42,600
But I didn't see her.

117
00:07:46,000 --> 00:07:48,120
Maybe I just imagined it.

118
00:07:50,120 --> 00:07:51,160
Probably not.

119
00:07:52,920 --> 00:07:54,439
She might be nearby.

120
00:07:55,639 --> 00:07:58,319
I'll have Wen Li look into it.

121
00:07:59,399 --> 00:08:00,240
Don't worry.

122
00:08:03,360 --> 00:08:06,079
Have something to eat first.

123
00:08:06,560 --> 00:08:07,680
Eat again?

124
00:08:09,480 --> 00:08:12,240
You've been feeding me
nonstop these days.

125
00:08:12,519 --> 00:08:13,639
I'm gaining weight.

126
00:08:15,279 --> 00:08:18,800
A little weight looks good on you.

127
00:08:23,399 --> 00:08:25,000
(If that really was Mom,)

128
00:08:26,000 --> 00:08:27,959
(why was she at the hospital?)

129
00:08:33,920 --> 00:08:39,890
♪So many words unsaid,
the deeper we fall, the more we fear♪

130
00:08:40,170 --> 00:08:47,770
♪Fate like a gamble,
locking us inside its game♪

131
00:08:47,820 --> 00:08:51,610
♪Hearts at play, truth and lies,
who could ever know♪

132
00:08:52,130 --> 00:08:55,410
♪Where this ends♪

133
00:08:55,410 --> 00:09:02,690
♪I try to walk away,
yet still step into the fire♪

134
00:09:02,690 --> 00:09:07,020
♪Your heartbeat pulls me under,
and I lose myself♪

135
00:09:07,060 --> 00:09:10,140
♪Love turns into pain♪

136
00:09:10,210 --> 00:09:14,330
♪Words betray us
until our eyes burn red♪

137
00:09:14,490 --> 00:09:17,970
♪Yet I still want you close♪

138
00:09:17,970 --> 00:09:22,140
♪Your tide breaks me,
and I fall for you again♪

139
00:09:22,140 --> 00:09:25,450
♪Even if love becomes nothing♪

140
00:09:25,450 --> 00:09:30,020
♪When love and hate fade
into the crowd and the ice melts♪

141
00:09:30,020 --> 00:09:36,330
♪Does it mean we could meet again?♪

142
